the faster the poison reacts.

1063
01:24:04,940 --> 01:24:07,147
Your poison is really strong.

1064
01:24:07,276 --> 01:24:08,778
- Get the vault.
- Yes.

1065
01:24:08,877 --> 01:24:11,050
- Everyone, let's go.
- Go.

1066
01:24:12,881 --> 01:24:14,053
Stop!

1067
01:24:16,318 --> 01:24:17,991
- You.
- Me?

1068
01:24:18,120 --> 01:24:19,690
I'm not poisoned.

1069
01:24:20,255 --> 01:24:22,064
When you threw the darts,

1070
01:24:22,157 --> 01:24:24,535
<i>I realized something was wrong</i>

1071
01:24:24,626 --> 01:24:27,163
<i>I held my breath and covered my nose.</i>

1072
01:24:27,796 --> 01:24:30,777
<i>When I saw you taking off your mask,
I knew it was safe to breathe.</i>

1073
01:24:30,866 --> 01:24:33,472
Otherwise, as you said,

1074
01:24:33,568 --> 01:24:34,876
I'd surely be dead now.

1075
01:24:34,970 --> 01:24:36,347
Give me the antidote.

1076
01:24:36,805 --> 01:24:39,081
- Don't give him...
- I...

1077
01:24:39,174 --> 01:24:40,744
That's okay.

1078
01:24:40,842 --> 01:24:42,344
I will. I will.

1079
01:24:45,714 --> 01:24:47,557
You...

1080
01:24:49,251 --> 01:24:51,026
Where's the antidote?

1081
01:24:59,461 --> 01:25:01,463
- Kill those madmen first.
- Okay.

1082
01:27:27,008 --> 01:27:29,181
- What happened?
- You were poisoned.

1083
01:27:29,277 --> 01:27:31,780
