to Szma Zhongyuan.

1084
01:27:36,418 --> 01:27:37,556
Stay back.

1085
01:27:38,119 --> 01:27:39,530
What do you want?

1086
01:27:41,189 --> 01:27:42,827
I'm giving you the antidote.

1087
01:28:01,409 --> 01:28:02,513
Stay back.

1088
01:28:04,212 --> 01:28:05,657
Look at this bottle.

1089
01:28:06,481 --> 01:28:07,585
What?

1090
01:28:11,253 --> 01:28:13,096
Yes, swallow it.

1091
01:28:15,524 --> 01:28:16,594
What?

1092
01:28:17,792 --> 01:28:19,100
Swallow it?

1093
01:28:26,268 --> 01:28:27,838
Yes, swallow it.

1094
01:28:45,854 --> 01:28:47,527
They're trying to cheat us.

1095
01:28:47,622 --> 01:28:49,863
They want to kill us.

1096
01:28:50,325 --> 01:28:52,805
I won't be cheated by you.

1097
01:29:05,707 --> 01:29:09,052
Brother, do you know who I am?

1098
01:29:09,311 --> 01:29:10,312
Who?

1099
01:29:10,412 --> 01:29:12,824
I'm the Bat Without Wings.

1100
01:29:13,281 --> 01:29:14,385
Really?

1101
01:29:15,784 --> 01:29:17,991
I can fly, too.

1102
01:29:22,157 --> 01:29:25,570
Can't you see I'm flying now?

1103
01:29:26,461 --> 01:29:30,375
I'm flying, flying, flying.

1104
01:29:30,966 --> 01:29:33,310
- Release Miss Szma's pressure point.
- Yes.

1105
01:29:36,938 --> 01:29:38,178
Follow me.

1106
01:29:40,609 --> 01:29:41,781
Hurry up.

1107
01:30:05,200 --> 01:30:07,680
Look, I'm the Bat Without Wings.

1108
01:30:07,769 --> 01:30:11,546
I can fly!

1109
01:30:11,640 --> 01:30:14,484
Dad, don't jump!

1110
01:30:14,576 --> 01:30:17,489
You don't believe that I can fly?

1111
01:30:18,113 --> 01:30:21,094
I'll show you that I can.

1112
01:30:22,150 --> 01:30:26,530
I'm flying...

1113
01:30:29,691 --> 01:30:33,138
Dad!

1114
01:30:37,098 --> 01:30:38,133
Dad!

1115
01:30:43,605 --> 01:30:44,640
Dad!

1116
01:30:48,910 --> 01:30:52,221
Dad. Dad.


